# Step 2: Create a project
# Step 3: Go to Settings → API in your dashboard
# Step 4: Copy the full values below (not the shortened ones!)
#
# Your current key appears incomplete - it should be 100+ characters!

# Replace "your_full_url_here" with your Supabase Project URL
# Example: https://abc123defghijk.supabase.co
